//第一段
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"> 
<title>css第一课</title> 
<style>
p
{
	color:blue;
	text-align:left;
} 
</style>
</head>

<body>
<p>这是css第一课</p>
<p>希望我能学好</p>
</body>
</html>

//第二段
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"> 
<title>css第一课</title> 
<style>
#para1
{
	text-align:center;
	color:purple;
} 
</style>
</head>

<body>
<p id="para1">开课</p>
<p>这句话不受上边设定影响</p>
</body>
</html>
